(\omega_2 + \theta_3)^{(2)} \wedge (\omega_2 + \theta_3)
= (\omega_2^{(2)} + 2\omega_2 \wedge \theta_3 + \theta_3^{(2)}) \wedge (\omega_2 + \theta_3) = (\omega_2^{(2)} + 2\omega_2 \wedge \theta_3) \wedge (\omega_2 + \theta_3)
= (\omega_2^{(3)} + 2\omega_2^{(2)} \wedge \theta_3 + \omega_2^{(2)} \wedge \theta_3 + 2\omega_2 \wedge \theta_3^{(2)}) = 3\omega_2^{(2)} \wedge \theta_3. \tag{10}
